n very helpful. After my first visit with Jeremy, the pain immediately started to lessen. His treatments over some time have gotten me to the point where I can lift weights again and do normal tasks. Jeremy is a fantastic massage therapist. He worked wonders for me and I can’t thank him enough!!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by K.T. (Kitchener) – Mobile App Developer</strong>\r\nI see Jeremy for deep tissue treatments to help with neck, shoulder, and back pain from sitting at a computer most of the day. He''s personable and professional, and his massages really help with my neck/shoulder/back pain. I''d strongly recommend seeing Jeremy if you''re looking for a deep tissue massage.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by SG (Kitchener) </strong>\r\nI only have good things to say about KW Massage. Jeremy is very personable and easy to schedule appointments with. I used to get terrible tension headaches, but monthly appointments with Jeremy have made them all but disappear!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by KOB (Kitchener) – Web Development/Home Renovations</strong>\r\nGetting deep tissue massage from Jeremy for the past 6 years has been an absolute life saver. Jeremy has been able to help me relieve many of my ailments and bodily pains. I competed in 2013 Jiu-Jitsu World Championships and Jeremy was one of the cornerstones of my coaching and therapy team. If you''re looking to have long term results that last, I would highly recommend using Jeremy and KW Massage. He also has a great website for booking appointments, it''s worth checking it out.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by S.D. (Kitchener) – Transport Operator </strong>\r\nJeremy at KW massage has been massaging my back, calve and shoulder for a few years. Recently I had developed knee pain. Im so glad I brought it to jeremys attention, he explained how it might be coming from my hip and thigh. Two treatments later and no more knee pain. He has taught me the right stretches to do to stop the pain from coming back. Jeremy loves what he does and is a great massage therapist, the best in Kitchener.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by A Google User </strong>\r\nGetting deep tissue massage from Jeremy for the past 4 years has been an absolute life saver. Jeremy has been able to help me relieve many of my ailments and bodily pains. If you''re looking to have long term results that last, I would highly recommend using Jeremy and KW Massage. He also has a great website for booking appointments, it''s worth checking it out.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n<b> </b>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="testimonialbox">\r\n<div class="testimonialinner">\r\n<div class="quotetop">\r\n<div class="quotebottom">\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><strong> by A Google User </strong>\r\nNot only does he care about what he does but Jeremy car