(338, 3, '2014-01-16 16:10:11', '2014-01-16 16:10:11', 'The Psoas muscle is a strong muscle at the front of your hip. It often affects your <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/stretching/general-guidelines-for-stretching">low back </a><span style="text-decoration: underline;">and </span>can cause pain. If you sit for long periods of time, be sure to <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JtnQHieEkqQ">stretch the Psoas muscle </a>often.\r\n\r\nBe sure to review to my <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/stretching/general-guidelines-for-stretching">General Guidelines for stretching </a>before doing any of the stretches I demonstrate and recommend. It’s always a good idea to see a <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/generalmassagetherapy/governance-of-massage-therapy">health care professional </a>before starting a new exercise program.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/JtnQHieEkqQ?rel=0" height="360" width="480" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe>', 'How to Stretch Psoas Muscle ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-stretch-psoase-muscle', '', 'http://www.kwmassage.com/stretching/general-guidelines-for-stretching\nhttp://www.kwmassage.com/generalmassagetherapy/governance-of-massage-therapy', '2014-01-23 17:27:00', '2014-01-23 17:27:00', '', 0, 'http://www.kwmassage.com/?p=338', 0, 'post', '', 0),
