(349, 3, '2014-01-16 16:26:49', '2014-01-16 16:26:49', 'No, I do not charge an initial consultation fee for <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/clinic-information">massage therapy treatments</a>.\r\n\r\nI have a simple one page <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Health-History.pdf" target="_blank">Health History</a> form for you to fill out, and I take 5 minutes or so to go over this form and get a general idea of what I’m treating before we begin. After reviewing your needs, we can get started right away, and any other information I can ask <a href="http://www.kwmassage.com/clinic-information" target="_blank">while I’m treating you</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/br953TUGKxs?rel=0" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe>', 'Do You Charge An Initial Consultation Fee For Massage Therapy Appointments?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'initial-consultation-fee', '', '\nhttp://www.kwmassage.com/clinic-information', '2014-01-23 17:32:55', '2014-01-23 17:32:55', '', 0, 'http://www.kwmassage.com/?p=349', 0, 'post', '', 0),
